The '''Qel-Droma''' family was a [[Force-sensitive/Legends|Force-sensitive]] [[Human/Legends|Human]] bloodline from [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]] that had produced a number of powerful [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] warriors in the era of the [[Old Sith Wars]]. 
[[Ulic Qel-Droma/Legends|Ulic]] and [[Cay Qel-Droma]], sons of [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Lien-Tsai Qel-Droma]]<ref name="TOTJC" />, were raised on Alderaan alongside their cousin, [[Duron Qel-Droma]].<ref name="KOTORCG">''[[Knights of the Old Republic Campaign Guide]]''</ref> All three [[Alderaanian/Legends|Alderaanians]] would eventually became [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knights]], though Ulic Qel-Droma would fall to the [[Dark side of the Force/Legends|dark side of the force]] and became a [[Dark Lord of the Sith/Legends|Dark Lord of the Sith]].<ref name="TEGTC" />
[[Sedriss QL]], born Qaga Lok, was [[Executor (Imperial rank)|Military Executor]] to the reborn [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] and a distant descendant of Ulic Qel-Droma.<ref name="FF">{{FactFile|85|SED 1-4|Exekutor Sedress (German Edition)}}</ref>
