==Behind the scenes==
The Alderaanian [[Frigate/Legends|frigate]] ''[[Qel-Droma]]'' shares a name with the Qel-Droma family, though no connection between the two has been established.<ref name="DBSB">{{DB|character|pelloscambras|Scrambas, Pello}}</ref>

